Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well have some fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they're gonna host something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Host something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Academy sponsored...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure Hunting... {lit: FABULOUS PRIZE}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orienteering Competition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa Yoshii has found some gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I haven't eaten like this in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumizuki Flour is every bit as delicious as I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes just like bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have no complaints if I could just get some jam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no room to complain in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess flour digests pretty quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fox Phi. Kisaragi Land's mascot character.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's very popular with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Kisara-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already explained it in the narration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever lost this is probably looking for it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it... I can't find it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good morning, Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for something I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my Phi strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a limited edition... They don't sell it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? It's right over-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, what now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fukuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme permission to do a summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! Just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might as well. Just remember, this is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty! Grab that strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Phi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ... That damn feedback system...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mrs. Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared the hell outta me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use Beings to wreak havoc like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to pick that strap up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you shouldn't be playing with toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to put it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your summoning permission has been suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beings are absolutely not to be used for violent purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violent!? I was just doing that for-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoned Beings are not toys for idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you frustrated? Why not try proving that you're not an idiot, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might just be able to get your hands on what you want, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the principal meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prizes are written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free meals for a year!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coupons for new video games!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also mentions "secret items"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Phi-Noin-Ain limited edition strap set?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.00,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this! This! This! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on Earth do you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do we win those prizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna search for them using this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to brag, but I'm awesome at finding treasure in RPGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are the test questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answers to the questions on these represent the coordinates for the checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We then exchange tickets for prizes at said checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get 'em if we don't answer the questions correctly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also first-come, first-serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into another team,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to settle it with a Summoning Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being cockblocked by everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec... I just need to get on a team with Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna announce the teams for the orienteering competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in my team...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji and Hideyoshi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji and Minami are in a team with Voyeur!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grouped all of the troublemakers together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to know what you guys have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's not exactly fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi is cute, so whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Yuuji is completely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the entire school day to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three questions in each set, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to the first one is the x coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y coordinate for the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And z for the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, in layman's terms, which floor it's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check this out! They're all multiple choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at multiple choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you not know my specialties?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Get a load of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I almost believed you for a second, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For math, I use the Striker Sigma V!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For modern Japanese, I use the Problem Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shining Answer for history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all accurate beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always just leave things to chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat them lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Striker Sigma V!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X coordinate: 652.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y coordinate: 237.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z coordinate: 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked on! It's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go fetch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they make a mistake writing the problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! It's a prize ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we drew first blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like our x and y were correct, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! Striker Sigma V is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more "amazing" for actually believing it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can redeem this for a year's worth of free desserts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split them between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this if we manage to find it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A premium ticket to Kisaragi Grand Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! You want to go with your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a chill down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer anything besides math!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart, Tsuchiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I skipped everything except health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These coordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to walk into the girls' changing room legally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's look for the prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a changing room, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to tidy this place up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not afraid of the guys seeing it, so it's pretty much a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to come here unless it's in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tsuchiya? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine... This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let me take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at how those idiots are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce the heavens! Problem... BREAKER!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coordinates point to around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the prize, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird... maybe I should try condensing it more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that basket...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I love 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Actually, I woke up early today to bake some chiffon cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I didn't know you could bake cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Problem Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've struck gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were such a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like I'm about to die...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be nice if you could all eat some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's four of you, so there's not enough to go around...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three chiffon cakes. Four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of us will live to see tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the first annual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...power level competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll decide it with rock paper scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki and Tsuchiya are sure taking their sweet time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! One more problem and my head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've solved them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at the answers I slaved over for you, Sissy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I compared the coordinates with the map,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered that the prize was hidden in your bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prepare to surrender your body and soul to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! The coordinates don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ministry of Education agrees! Don't even bother trying to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's make an even bigger mistake together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.33,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if they have the time to host these damn things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't they use it to accelerate the course material instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coordinates point to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yoshii's shoebox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone sees me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to think that I'm sneaking a love letter into Yoshii's shoebox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I'm just here to get my tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...! Won't it look like I'm stealing someone else's love letter to Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I only want the treasure inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what others think! I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't the contents of Yoshii's shoebox be considered a treasure by some!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never escape this guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rock, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I had much to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what the prize is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this isn't what we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They pulled one over on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could random chance pull one over on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to change the angle of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:58.25,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's going to increase the accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually answered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's right, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to end up somewhere crazy because you screwed it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Yuuji's answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! There really is one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you manage to solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose a set with problems that I could solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the bottom of the class with regards to test scores, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that hard to convince you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A premium couples' ticket to Kisaragi Grand Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All couples are invited to participate in our mock-wedding event.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go with Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd turn that "mock" wedding into the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show me shit like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, are you free this Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ticket says it's for couples!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Do you hate me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does God hate me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing I can do at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These words hold a deeper meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not know this, but, in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a legend saying that you'll be blessed if you confess beneath a legendary tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's only one thing "legendary tree" could be referring to at this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It refers to the legendary beauty, Hideyoshi Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:36.47,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Kinoshita can be also read as "under a tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you'll be blessed if you confess to Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Hideyoshi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong on so many levels that I don't even know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:43.31,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? If that's true, we can all confess to Hideyoshi without fear of being persecuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, looks like it's not gonna work out for us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty unfair for idiots like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many prizes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the secret items are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Phi straps are still available!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only problems left are pretty fucking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you just gonna walk around randomly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Randomly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'll just answer all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fill in every possible coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a prize at places where the x and y axes intersect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to check all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of places to look through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know long this would take...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This game is based around searching high and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No harm in trying. Not like we can solve the problems anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show them how idiots do things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you go to the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, you go to the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The janitor's closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Occupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The changing rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The women's bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somebody in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fish tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god it's empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, we didn't find shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's one place left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere you could hide stuff there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's found the strap yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be hidden somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi, you don't need to answer problems to-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? I found this place after solving all of the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules say that we can use a Summoning Battle to take that ticket by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're way too strong for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we'd have to go up against them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to get your asses kicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at these! There's three in a set, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki is gonna love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the secret items?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what these do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Bracelets. The activation phrase is "Awaken".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can summon our Beings without a teacher's permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The range is kind of limited, but this is still pretty sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one whose clothes got torn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, is yours okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that only dumbasses can use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dumbass too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're a super dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.39,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, the ultimate dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dumbass to rule all dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots are like scissors - it's all about how you use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night turns to dawn, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question six:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please list the different types of medleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anisong medley, oldies medley, pigeon cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like pigeon cookies myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Me and Pool and Swimsuit Paradise and.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.41,0:23:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on the test.
