Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:44.19,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.38,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFF3BA&}Meeting someone else is the easy way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:05.04,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HEBD5FE&}I knew what I would say before they even asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HB1FFB2&}Do I look lovestruck enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:09.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HC9E4FF&}I'm not gonna lose my cool, love's at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:12.84,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCAC7FF&}Study! Study! Study! It keeps me up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.47,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFC9EB&}I've got a genius inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.06,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HA0E6FF&}It'd be great if my dreams came true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:20.31,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD6C3CB&}because I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.90,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD5CDFF&}Perfect area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.61,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCDFFDC&}I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:32.20,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFFED3&}I can hear your voice from the perfect area ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.49,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HE8D4FF&}Fly! I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.41,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HBBECFF&}Yeah, that's me, the person you just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:40.75,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFCABF&}Are we still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.92,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HABFFC7&}I flunked our friendship test, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.21,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&H889DF8&}No! I'll take it again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFD8BF&}Come on, gimme another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:53.68,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFEBBF&}Something better awaits us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:02:00.18,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD7C3FD&}A better life awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.23,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}Never, never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:47.86,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:48.82,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}Never give up!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}It's a time of peace now that school's out.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.81,0:22:24.73,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}If I were to describe her, she's a real angel!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.74,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}Then came a notice that shattered my fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.49,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}It said I had to stay afterschool! It's like hell!!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}I was talking about it with my friends, and I said,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.91,0:22:36.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}"No way anyone's that stupid!!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.00,0:22:39.92,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}But deep inside me,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.04,0:22:42.38,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}I was shouting out,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.63,0:22:44.13,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}"I AM THAT STUPID!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.26,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}That sign in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}that says "Monthly"...{or "Tsukigime"}
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.84,0:22:55.97,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}I always thought that was the company's name.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.64,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.36,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Stupidity's a character! A real man!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.28,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Our common sense is the lack thereof!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.65,0:23:08.32,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}We don't need rules in our fucking world!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.36,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}Eat steak out every night, overthrow the mass!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.74,0:23:17.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Take a look, the sun that rose from the west is setting back down!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.79,0:23:20.83,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Run home, it's almost dinner!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.50,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
